name: VIBES
description:
To feel the magic of vibration is the essence of its fabric and to hear the voice of its spirit. Holy are the intervals between the shapes and colors of sound their number an infinite eight. A master of manifest moods between moons suns and stars in rhythm and beat the repeat of life’s heart. To start and begin and to become a part, to hear it’s a game rolled dice tricks of high art. The code and the road and the table before you the audience rise and applaud and implore you. Can you hear a song that is older than time, master the elements, grasp riddle and rhyme?
